        {
            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/120011256?u=9b1c1de5a62d4cc8a73582b6a58232dcfcca3188&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Description</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Removes unnecessary argument from the TextEncoder.encode call. The encode method accepts only an <a href=\"https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-textencoder\" rel=\"nofollow\">optional string argument</a> .</p>\n\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Motivation</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">correct technical issues on TextEncoder.encode method call</p>\n\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Additional details</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">The example on <a href=\"https://github.com/mdn/dom-examples/blob/main/streams/simple-writer/index.html\">dom-examples</a> doesn't use that argument.<br>\nThe <a href=\"https://encoding.spec.whatwg.org/#interface-textencoder\" rel=\"nofollow\">Encoding Api Spec</a> says that the method only accepts an optional string arguement.</p>\n\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Related issues and pull requests</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\"><span class=\"issue-keyword tooltipped tooltipped-se\" aria-label=\"This pull request closes issue #38824.\">Fixes</span> <a class=\"issue-link js-issue-link\" data-error-text=\"Failed to load title\" data-id=\"2950597238\" data-permission-text=\"Title is private\" data-url=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/38824\" data-hovercard-type=\"issue\" data-hovercard-url=\"/mdn/content/issues/38824/hovercard\" href=\"https://github.com/mdn/content/issues/38824\">#38824</a></p>\n\n\n",
