            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/692547?u=fe2b55b86649fb5088aab030fe3c1c964c8c7496&v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Description</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">Change numbers in the example to clearly demonstrate <code class=\"notranslate\">tabular-nums</code>.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Motivation</h3>\n<p dir=\"auto\">With this change, readers can see that digits are constant-width only when using <code class=\"notranslate\">tabular-nums</code>.</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Additional details</h3>\n\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Related issues and pull requests</h3>\n\n\n\n",
