            "content_html": "<img src=\"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/373675?v=4\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\" alt=\"\"/><br/>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Description</h3>\n\n<p dir=\"auto\">Use <code class=\"notranslate\">Object.hasOwn</code> on undefined and null property values</p>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Motivation</h3>\n\n<ul dir=\"auto\">\n<li>In my experience, the output of <code class=\"notranslate\">Object.hasOwn</code> on <code class=\"notranslate\">undefined</code>/<code class=\"notranslate\">null</code> property values can be unexpected, so I wanted to document it in the example.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Additional details</h3>\n\n<h3 dir=\"auto\">Related issues and pull requests</h3>\n\n\n\n",
